FIG. 5 is a circuit diagram for illustrating a defective current;


FIG. 6 is a schematic block diagram of a DRAM according to one embodiment of the present invention;


FIG. 7 is a series of timing diagrams illustrating a refresh operation of the DRAM of FIG. 6;


FIG. 8 is a circuit diagram of a clamp address decision circuit of the present invention;


FIG. 9 is a chart illustrating the operation of the clamp address decision circuit of FIG. 8;


FIG. 10 is a circuit diagram of a block selection circuit of the present invention;


FIG. 11 is a circuit diagram of a precharge control circuit and an equalizer circuit of the present invention; and


FIG. 12 is a circuit diagram of a redundancy decision circuit of the present invention.
